transcripts.text: In 2016, Marco Rubio blocked a new Supreme Court judge saying the people should get a voice in an election year.
In the last year of a president's term, there should not be a Supreme Court nominee.

Now, days before the election, Rubio supports rushing through a new judge, but refuses to pass COVID relief to help struggling families and businesses in Florida.  Call Marco Rubio and tell him to pass COVID relief now and let the people's voice be heard on the Supreme Court.  Senator Marco Rubio is letting Florida down.
